1.0.name: wordpress/san-francisco
1.0.description: A free SEO and Mobile Optimised WordPress Theme.  This theme automatically resizes and realigns iteself to fit to any screen width.  Beautiful when viewing on a mobile device with a smaller screen or on a large desktop screen.
